abstract: Dallas County district attorney's office says grand jury will hear domestic violence complaint against former Cleveland Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel; other pro football news noted.
lead_paragraph: A domestic violence complaint accusing the former Cleveland Browns quarterback Johnny Manziel of beating his ex-girlfriend will be presented to a Dallas County grand jury.

headline.main: Manziel Case Headed to Grand Jury
